    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将他们的世界编织为书本，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >少女坐在书桌前品着咖啡邀你一同阅读。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是作为她的朗诵者，将世界再一次演绎出来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亦或是尝试反抗书中的命运，肆意修改故事的结局呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽说是你的自由，但后果自负。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                   ——SisselA Kayla</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >失去记忆的“我”在一座图书之都中醒来，面前的白发少女邀请我为她朗诵书本。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次开始朗诵，“我”都进入书本中所描绘的世界之中成为不是“我”的某人亲历整个故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而“我”也拥有被少女称为“再演”的权利，以“我”的意志改变角色的行动将故事引导至不同的结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1849570/extras/5eddef56b34a24429e6d759648924ec8.avif?t=1770902878\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现已上线UnityBeta版更新！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前KRKR端和UnityYBeta版同时存在，KRKR端拥有3个完整已完结的小故事</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unity端将对这些故事进行重构并保持更新，KRKR端将不再进行更新</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前故事中的CV：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回忆之物：米糊zzZ 、柴豆bAME </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >绑架犯与少女：柴豆bAME 、上檠</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DLC1 地狱依存症：白灯不拖更 子刷子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爱发电支持制作：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >交流QQ群：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >327915520</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——————————————————</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >素材源：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔王魂</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >煉獄庭園</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DOVA-SYNDROME</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dead End Wonder</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixabay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >きまぐれアフター.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >KNT graphics：矢神ニーソ『</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小森　平</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >効果音g</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\